  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/892080884d6e7e8540a415a4d0ea4a95.poster.avif?t=1728958823\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/892080884d6e7e8540a415a4d0ea4a95.webm?t=1728958823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/892080884d6e7e8540a415a4d0ea4a95.mp4?t=1728958823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of Angel Raphael in this immersive and action-packed first-person dungeon crawler. Travel through 24 floors, each presenting a new challenge to overcome with new demons to fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in intense combat against a variety of demonic enemies, with the strategy and strength behind them increasing with each new floor. Uncover hidden side quests that offer new power to destroy anything in your path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/c794cb0c1fb202a16289711fa601dd57.poster.avif?t=1728958823\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/c794cb0c1fb202a16289711fa601dd57.webm?t=1728958823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/c794cb0c1fb202a16289711fa601dd57.mp4?t=1728958823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the drain combat system!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on loads of demon side quests to get new armor, weapons, and skills!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel the 24 floors and discover all the hidden secrets!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against 157 unique enemies and bosses!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10–20 hours worth of gameplay.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/d95b72d49a4d82589bfcaac0064d9a98.poster.avif?t=1728958823\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/d95b72d49a4d82589bfcaac0064d9a98.webm?t=1728958823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/d95b72d49a4d82589bfcaac0064d9a98.mp4?t=1728958823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you rise to the challenge and defeat Asmodeus?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/892080884d6e7e8540a415a4d0ea4a95.poster.avif?t=1728958823\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/892080884d6e7e8540a415a4d0ea4a95.webm?t=1728958823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/892080884d6e7e8540a415a4d0ea4a95.mp4?t=1728958823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of Angel Raphael in this immersive and action-packed first-person dungeon crawler. Travel through 24 floors, each presenting a new challenge to overcome with new demons to fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in intense combat against a variety of demonic enemies, with the strategy and strength behind them increasing with each new floor. Uncover hidden side quests that offer new power to destroy anything in your path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/c794cb0c1fb202a16289711fa601dd57.poster.avif?t=1728958823\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/c794cb0c1fb202a16289711fa601dd57.webm?t=1728958823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/c794cb0c1fb202a16289711fa601dd57.mp4?t=1728958823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the drain combat system!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on loads of demon side quests to get new armor, weapons, and skills!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel the 24 floors and discover all the hidden secrets!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against 157 unique enemies and bosses!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10–20 hours worth of gameplay.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/d95b72d49a4d82589bfcaac0064d9a98.poster.avif?t=1728958823\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/d95b72d49a4d82589bfcaac0064d9a98.webm?t=1728958823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2912530/extras/d95b72d49a4d82589bfcaac0064d9a98.mp4?t=1728958823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you rise to the challenge and defeat Asmodeus?</p>",
